            <div><img style="width: 100px; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; margin-bottom: 5px; " src="/assets/icons/logo_noText.svg" alt="portlogue-logo"/></div>
            <span class="footer-desc-span">Sharing and browsing personal websites made easy!</span>
            <p class="footer-desc-p">Showcase and share your wordpress, wix,
                weebly, and shopify websites with portlogue. Portlogue stores your websites in a single account and displays it upon clicking on your 
                profile. Join a community where it's all about 
                sharing and exploring personal websites.</p>
